{
  "description": "Mistakebook hooks: correction detection, notebook capture hints, Ascended Mode escalation, scholar preflight, compaction checkpoint, session restore, subagent memory injection, and hit metrics",
  "hooks": {
    "UserPromptSubmit": [
      {
        "matcher": "你这里错了|这不对|重新改|我来纠正你|我教你一遍|你又犯同样的错|还没改对|你没有吃透|按我说的改|这个回答有问题|这个地方你改坏了|你还是没明白我的意思|启动错题集|写入错题集|写入记事本|记一下这个事项|这个不是错题但要记住|mistakebook",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/correction-trigger.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "你需要根据你见过最有效的方法来处理这个问题|用你见过最有效的方法|见过最有效的方法|我都纠正你两次了还是不对|你已经改了两轮还是没抓到重点|/ascended|ascended",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/ascended-trigger.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/scholar-preflight-trigger.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PreCompact": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/lifecycle-pre-compact.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostCompact": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/lifecycle-post-compact.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SubagentStart": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/lifecycle-subagent-start.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SubagentStop": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/lifecycle-subagent-stop.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SessionEnd": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/lifecycle-session-end.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "matcher": "compact",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/session-restore.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "startup|resume",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/session-restore.sh",
            "timeout": 5
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
